org.horrabin.horrorss
Class RssItemBean

java.lang.Object
  org.horrabin.horrorss.RssItemBean
public class RssItemBean
extends java.lang.Object

The RssItemBean object represents the element item in an RSS feed. Valid for the RSS 2.0, RDF and ATOM specifications

Author:
Fernando Fornieles

Constructor Detail

RssItemBean

public RssItemBean(int rssType)
Create a new RssItemBean.
  • If rssType=0 the feed is RDF
  • If rssType=1 the feed is RSS 2.0
  • If rssType=2 the feed is ATOM

Parameters:
rssType - Sets the specification type (RSS 2.0, RDF or ATOM)
